# --- CST Studio Suite ---

# Ignore the entire project results folder 
# (This contains Model, ModelCache, and Result subfolders)
# If your file is ProjectName.cst, this ignores the folder ProjectName/
*/Model/
*/ModelCache/
*/Result/
*/Temp/

# Ignore specific large binary and log files
*.rtp
*.rtp~
*.lok
*.bak
*.log
*.pax
*.user

# If you want to be aggressive and just keep the source:
# This ignores the folder named after your project entirely
# Replace 'ProjectName' with your actual filename or use a wildcard
# [ProjectName]/
